text.tspan: Certain cats are overlooked due to colour or age. We
are struggeling to to find a home for these cats, which
is a shame, because they are as good a pet as others.
Volunteer at the cat center in Archway
A problem I see often is people trying to oversell the
animal to a potential owner. It often backfires!
I often send booklets and guides to educate people,
especially if they never had a pet before
Runs a dog adoption service in Shangai
